{"about_the_game":"<i>Demons are coming!</i> is a bullet hell rougelite shooter where you fight a high variety of demons that occupied your holy land. Use the upgrades you find to your advantage and create your ideal guns to help you kill the most terrifying monsters.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/clip1.gif?t=1719500424\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Shape the terrain</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/clip4.gif?t=1719500424\" /><br>Destroy enemy cover to get closer to your opponents. Be careful because enemies can also put you out of position and make you an easy target.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Parry your opponents</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/clip3.gif?t=1719500424\" /><br>Deflecting enemy bullets can give you an edge against these filthy demons. This skill takes time to master, but once you do, no hellish creature can stop you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Upgrade your gun</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/clip2.gif?t=1719500424\" /><br>You have 2 guns, each containg slots for your gun modifications. Equipping upgrades will drastically change the way your weapon feels and functions. It will make each of your runs feel distinct and unique!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2702030/4b184c2c95589569f8a00b5020256fac50a7f8cd.jpg"},{"name":"Quick Learner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2702030/f31ae5440b5a745e315a18023c61da5e5d76b900.jpg"},{"name":"Demon Slayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2702030/c20c4b1387fa2220e5154a03c41353bb3595ef6a.jpg"},{"name":"Creature Slayer","path":